# Move Layout Components to Components Directory

The goal is to restructure the project by moving reusable UI components from `src/layouts` to `src/components`, leaving only actual page layouts in `src/layouts`.

## User Review Required

> [!WARNING]
> `src/components/Footer.astro` already exists. I plan to rename the existing one to `Footer.original.astro` and replace it with the one from `src/layouts/Footer.astro`, which seems to be the main one used by the layouts.

